{"type":"message","id":"57528cdd","parentId":"0c8e435a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T07:50:11.338Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The realtime-data.txt file appears to be an image. Let me check its content. But first, I need to understand the workflow:\n\n1. Check if market is closed using tushare-data skill\n2. Clear realtime-data.txt if not empty\n3. Get real-time stock data\n4. Filter based on alert rules\n5. Send alerts via Feishu\n\nLet me first check the watchlist to see what stocks we're monitoring, then use the tushare-data skill to get market status and real-time data.\n\nFirst, let me read the watchlist file.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_10ddddca11104aaea23df0ee","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773129008896}}
